               <p>Doris Kleilein (Dipl.-Ing.) is an architect, author and editor with 25 years publishing experience in the field of architecture and urbanism. Before joining JOVIS in 2019, she was an editor of Bauwelt magazine in Berlin. In 2022 she was a research fellow at the Thomas Mann House in Los Angeles.</p>                      </div>                     </div>                    </div>                   </section>                  </div>                 </div>                </div>               </div>              </div>             </section>            </div>           </div>          </div>         </div>        </div>       </section>      </div>     </div>    </div>   </div>  </section> </div>


